Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:43.49,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Detarame na uta wo utai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:47.37,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}“nan da yo, sore” tte warau
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:52.12,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Tabi wa tsuzuku to omotta
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:07.14,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Kanashimi ga tsuzuku michi wo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:11.14,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Ato dore dake arukeba ii?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:15.40,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Furikaettemo mou mienai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:19.53,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Kagayaku no wa sugita hi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:27.16,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Onaji toki omoidashite hiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:34.42,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Hora kimi to miageteta nagareboshi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:38.38,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Tsurete ikou ano uta wo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:42.42,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Ano toki wo ano yoru wo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:46.47,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Bokura ga iru itsudemo aeru
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:50.47,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Sabishikunai yo soko ni iru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:52.27,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Wasure wa shinai hibike
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:59.40,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Kono natsukashii senritsu ga
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:03.78,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}bokura ni todoku made
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:38.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Kita sedang menuju ke kota itu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:43.49,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Sambil menyanyikan lagu tak karuan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:47.37,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}kau berkata "nada apaan itu?” dan tertawa
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:52.12,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Kita mengira perjalanan akan terus berlanjut
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:07.14,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Jalan ini dipenuhi dengan kesedihan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:11.14,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Sampai kapan kita akan terus berjalan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:15.40,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Berbalik ke belakang, namun sudah tak terlihat
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:19.53,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Masa gemilang dulu t'lah berakhir
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:27.16,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Kita teringat masa-masa yang sama
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:34.42,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Ingat, bintang jatuh yang kita lihat berdua dulu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:38.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Ayo kita bawa lagu itu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:42.42,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Momen itu, malam itu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:46.47,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Kita masih ada di sini, bisa bertemu kapanpun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:50.47,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Aku tidak kesepian, karena kau ada di sana
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:54.10,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Jangan kau lupakan, teruslah menggema
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:59.40,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Sampai melodi nostalgia ini
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:03.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}dapat kita jangkau.
